<p>Create Graphs using the built in editor.<p>
<p>Just click the mouse and drag to create nodes, and click in a node and drag to create a link.</p>
<p>Graphical styles are easily set using the graphical properties side panel, which can be hidden when you don't need it.</p>
<p>And edit the node and link properties in the left side panel, which can also be hidden when you don't need it.</p>
